Package org.apache.jena.ontapi.common

Class OntPersonalities

java.lang.Object
org.apache.jena.ontapi.common.OntPersonalities
public class OntPersonalities extends Object
Settings and personalities that are used for constructing OntModel. An access point to several predefined Ontology Personality constants.
